CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 22, 1957, pg. A9 reads:"Letsche Honors Athletes - Letsche School honored the members of its basketball teams, the Varsity and All-Stars recently by presenting the boys with letters and trophies, in recognition of their fine sportsmanship....Bottom photo: trophy winners, center: Eugene Jackson, left to right Mr. Geyer, coach; Ellis Montague, David Webb, David Jackson, John Wilkins, Otis Killings, Eli Sturdivant, Elbert Millender and A.J. Stepnick, supervisor of physical education. Mr. Stopnick made the presentation. -Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of trophy winners, center: Eugene Jackson; from left: coach J.D. Geyer, Ellis Montague, David Webb, David Jackson, John Wilkins, Otis Killings, Eli Sturdivant, Elbert Millender, and physical education supervisor A.J. Stepnick, posed in Letsche School
